Package: etc2comp
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Texture to ETC2 compressor
 Etc2Comp is a command line tool that converts textures (e.g. bitmaps) into the ETC2 format.
